# ADR 0005 — Locked baseline: 8 cloud + 3 self-hosted, March-2026 cutoff

**Date:** 2026-07-04
**Status:** Accepted (per user message 2026-07-04)
**Supersedes:** ADR 0003 §3 (which proposed Qwen3.8B AWQ as T2 workhorse — rejected by user)
**Author:** Forge (claude-code session, with corrections from user push-back on rounds 1–4)

---

## 1. Decision

Lock the baseline matrix to **7 cloud + 3 self-hosted models**, with a **March-2026 recency cutoff** for both lists. Everything else is "candidate for later" and not in the eval matrix until it gets its own ADR.

**Drop history (per user 2026-07-04):** `ibm-granite/granite-4.0-h-micro` was the only cloud entry below the March-2026 cutoff (HF last_modified 2025-11-03). User confirmed drop. The remaining 7 cloud picks all pass the recency cutoff.

